        <source>processTransaction(_transaction: CM_TITransaction; _camProtocol: CM_CamProtocol; _camAgent : CM_CamControllerAgent input; _camFile: CM_CamFile input) updating;
/* 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Created:     J Harliwich               

 Purpose:   This subclass won't do any further filtering like some of the
			other subclasses, all filtering must be on the query. Simpler
			that way.

 Changed On Changed By	Reason
 ---------- ----------	--------------------------------------------------
 11/05/2010	cnwcs5		PAR 23967 - record a CAMS INFO transaction 
 12/05/2010	cnwcs5		par 23967 - change _camFile paremeter to be input not io so as to correctly reflect its usage
 25/08/2010	cnwdad1		CCMS 1903 (PAR #24065) - new Info EDI Sent transaction (to replace Information trx). 
 18 Jul 2012	cnwrs1	CCMS 1269 CAMS remove CM_CamTask
 04/02/2013	cnwcs5		CCMS SFW 1294 /par 30855 - remove code that created CM_InfoEDISent transaction (now done when history created)
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*/
vars
	
begin
	// does nothing - should probably be removed and code that calls it
	// just here for consistency
epilog

end;
</source>
